    "headline": "Hirundo Joins HPE’s Unleash AI Partner Program to Help Enterprises Reduce Model Risk with Machine Unlearning",
    "summary": "SAN JOSE, Calif., March 17, 2026--Hirundo, a Machine Unlearning platform provider, today announced it has joined the HPE Unleash AI partner program. Now, customers leveraging HPE’s portfolio of integrated AI solutions can use Hirundo’s machine unlearning capabilities to help identify, and remove, unwanted or sensitive training signals from AI models—supporting safety, compliance and model performance objectives across the AI lifecycle.",
